{
  "title": "Warm Smoky Norwegian Beet Stew",
  "description": "This hearty Norwegian stew features earthy beets, smoky flavors, and pillowy textures, making it an energizing and comforting dish. It is kosher-friendly and perfect for a cold winter's night.",
  "cuisine": "Norwegian",
